T_IodineWizard_Q43_MaximumVolume_Guidanc.Source:
The calculated contrast volume will never be higher than this value.

Set this to the highest amount that you are comfortable injecting.
T_IodineWizard_Q43_MaximumVolume_Guidanc.Translation:
Le volume de produit de contraste calculé ne sera jamais supérieur à cette valeur.

Définissez cette valeur sur la quantité la plus élevée qu’il est possible d’injecter selon vous.

T_IodineWizard_Q43_MaximumVolume_Implica.Source: The maximum iodine load that any patient would ever receive would be {1}.
T_IodineWizard_Q43_MaximumVolume_Implica.Translation: La carga máxima de yodo que un paciente recibiría en cualquier circunstancia sería de {1}.

T_IodineWizard_Q43_MaximumVolume_Questio.Source: What is the largest volume of contrast media that you would deliver using this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q43_MaximumVolume_Questio.Translation: Quel est le volume de produit de contraste le plus élevé que vous pourriez administrer avec ce protocole ?

T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Guidanc.Source:
The calculated contrast volume will never be lower than this value.

Set this to the lowest volume that you think should always be delivered. Set this to 0ml to give the most dosing flexibility.
T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Guidanc.Translation:
A kiszámított kontrasztanyag-mennyiség értéke soha nem lesz alacsonyabb ennél az értéknél.

Állítsa ezt arra a legalacsonyabb mennyiségre, amelyet minden esetben megfelelőnek tart a bevitelre. Állítsa ezt 0 ml értékre az optimális adagolási rugalmasság biztosítása érdekében.

T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Implica.Source: There is no minimum volume that might affect the calculated iodine load or delivery rate.
T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Implica.Translation: Non esiste un volume minimo che potrebbe influire sul carico di iodio o sulla velocità di somministrazione dello iodio calcolati.

T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Implica.Source: This minimum might increase the iodine load or delivery rate from the calculated value.
T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Implica.Translation: Questo valore minimo potrebbe aumentare il carico di iodio o la velocità di somministrazione dello iodio rispetto al valore calcolato.

T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Questio.Source: What is the minimum amount of contrast media that should always delivered by this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Questio.Translation: Qual è la quantità minima di mezzo di contrasto che dovrebbe essere somministrata sempre utilizzando questo protocollo?

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Guidance.Source: Scans are either triggered using a fixed delay from the start of the contrast injection or are triggered using bolus tracking.
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Guidance.Translation: Les acquisitions sont soit déclenchées selon un délai fixe à partir du début de l’injection du produit de contraste, soit déclenchées par suivi du bolus.

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Source: More information is needed about how injection duration is handled when using bolus tracking.
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Translation: Требуется дополнительная информация о том, как обрабатывается продолжительность инъекции при использовании отслеживания болюсного введения.

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Source: This means that the flow rate will vary per patient but the injection duration will stay constant at {0} seconds.
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Translation: Oznacza to, że prędkość przepływu będzie różniła się w zależności od pacjenta, ale czas trwania wstrzykiwania pozostanie niezmienny i będzie wynosił {0} sekund.

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Question.Source: How do you handle scan timing for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Question.Translation: Jakie jest postępowanie w przypadku czasu skanowania dla niniejszego protokołu?

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Guidanc.Source: Fixed durations are preferred in order to keep timing as consistent as possible.
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Guidanc.Translation: A preferált lehetőség a fix időtartam, annak biztosítása érdekében, hogy az időzítés a lehető legkonzisztensebb legyen.

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Source: This means the flow rate will be kept constant at {0} and the duration will vary based on the iodine load.
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Translation: Это означает, что расход введения будет оставаться постоянным на уровне {0}, а продолжительность будет варьироваться в зависимости от йодной нагрузки.

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Source: This means that the flow rate will vary per patient but the injection duration will stay constant at {0} seconds.
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Translation: Oznacza to, że prędkość przepływu będzie różniła się w zależności od pacjenta, ale czas trwania wstrzykiwania pozostanie niezmienny i będzie wynosił {0} sekund.

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Questio.Source: When using bolus tracking, a consistent injection duration is still recommended. Is it okay to use a fixed injection duration for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Questio.Translation: При использовании отслеживания болюсного введения по-прежнему рекомендуется постоянная продолжительность инъекции. Можно ли использовать фиксированную продолжительность инъекции для этого протокола?

T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_G.Source:
The calculated flow rate will never be higher than this value.

Set this to the highest rate with which you are comfortable.
T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_G.Translation:
Den beregnede strømningshastigheten vil aldri være høyere enn denne verdien.

Still denne til den høyeste hastigheten som du er komfortabel med.

T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_I.Source: This maximum will not be exceeded, but if set too low, it will affect the calculated protocol and scan timing.
T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_I.Translation: Cette valeur maximale ne sera pas dépassée, mais si la valeur du réglage est trop basse, cela affectera le protocole calculé et la synchronisation de l’acquisition.

T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_Q.Source: What is the highest flow rate that you would use for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_Q.Translation: Jaka jest maksymalna prędkość przepływu, która mogłaby być zastosowana dla tego protokołu?

T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_G.Source:
The calculated flow rate will never be lower than this value.

Set this to the lowest rate that you think should be used.  Set this to 0 ml/s to give the most dosing flexibility.
T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_G.Translation:
Расчетный расход введения никогда не будет ниже этого значения.

Установите минимальный расход введения, который, по вашему мнению, следует использовать.  Установите это значение на 0 мл/с, чтобы обеспечить максимальную гибкость дозирования.
T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_G.ExampleContext: ml/s; must be kept relatively short; abbreviate as needed.

T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_I.Source: There is no minimum flow rate that might increase the calculated one.
T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_I.Translation: Nie ma minimalnej wartości przepływu, która mogłaby spowodować wzrost tej obliczonej.

T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_I.Source: This minimum will be used, but if set too high, it will affect the calculated protocol and scan timing.
T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_I.Translation: Cette valeur minimale ne sera pas utilisée, mais si la valeur du réglage est trop élevée, cela affectera le protocole calculé et la synchronisation de l’acquisition.

T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_Q.Source: What is the minimum flow rate that you feel is required for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_Q.Translation: Was ist die minimale Flussrate, die Ihrer Meinung nach für dieses Protokoll erforderlich wäre?

T_IodineWizardStatus_AlreadyAGenerator_D.Source: This protocol is already a Smart Protocol and does not need to be converted.
T_IodineWizardStatus_AlreadyAGenerator_D.Translation: Dieses Protokoll ist bereits ein intelligentes Protokoll und muss nicht konvertiert werden.

T_IodineWizardStatus_ContrastAndSalineRa.Source: This protocol has different flow rates for the contrast and saline phases and therefore cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols with constant flow rates can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_ContrastAndSalineRa.Translation: Ce protocole comporte différents débits pour les phases du produit de contraste et du sérum physiologique et par conséquent, il ne peut pas être converti en un protocole basé sur l’iode.  Seuls les protocoles d’injection de produit de contraste et de sérum physiologique biphasiques simples avec des débits constants peuvent être convertis pour le moment.

T_IodineWizardStatus_DelayPhasesNotSuppo.Source: This protocol has a delay phase and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_DelayPhasesNotSuppo.Translation: Ce protocole comporte une phase de délai et il ne peut pas être converti en un protocole à base d’iode.  Seuls les protocoles d’injection de produit de contraste et de sérum physiologique biphasiques simples peuvent être convertis pour le moment.

T_IodineWizardStatus_DualFlowPhasesNotSu.Source: This protocol has a DualFlow phase and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol. Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_DualFlowPhasesNotSu.Translation: Questo protocollo prevede una fase DualFlow e non può essere convertito in un protocollo basato sullo iodio.  Questo protocollo non può essere convertito in un protocollo basato sullo idio. Al momento è possibile convertire solo i protocolli di iniezione per soluzione fisiologica e per mezzo di contrasto bifase.

T_IodineWizardStatus_FirstPhaseMustBeCon.Source: The first phase of this protocol is not a contrast phase.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_FirstPhaseMustBeCon.Translation: La première phase de ce protocole n’est pas une phase de produit de contraste.  Ceci ne peut pas être converti en un protocole à base d’iode.  Actuellement, seuls les protocoles d’injection de produit de contraste et de sérum physiologique biphasiques simples peuvent être convertis.

T_IodineWizardStatus_HasAModifier_Descri.Source: This protocol has a kVp Ruleset associated with it.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_HasAModifier_Descri.Translation: Этот протокол имеет связанный с ним набор правил для пикового анодного напряжения.  На данный момент можно преобразовать только простые двухфазные протоколы введения контрастного средства и физиологического раствора.

T_IodineWizardStatus_HasTestInjection_De.Source: This protocol has a Test Injection.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_HasTestInjection_De.Translation: Questo protocollo prevede un'iniezione test.  Questo protocollo non può essere convertito in un protocollo basato sullo idio.  Al momento è possibile convertire solo i protocolli di iniezione per soluzione fisiologica e per mezzo di contrasto bifase.

T_IodineWizardStatus_NoContrastsDefined_.Source: Go to Admin/Contrasts on the injector to create contrast types before attempting to convert a protocol.
T_IodineWizardStatus_NoContrastsDefined_.Translation: Прежде чем пытаться преобразовать протокол, перейдите в раздел «Администрирование» > «Контрастные средства» на инъекторе, чтобы создать типы контрастного средства.

T_IodineWizardStatus_NotLicensed_Descrip.Source: Iodine based protocols (CENT-IOD) are not licensed.
T_IodineWizardStatus_NotLicensed_Descrip.Translation: I protocolli basati sullo iodio (CENT-IOD) non sono concessi in licenza.

T_IodineWizardStatus_ReadyToAskQuestions.Source: This protocol can be converted an equivalent iodine based protocol by answering a series of questions about how it is typically used.  When complete, the new protocol can be saved with a new name.
T_IodineWizardStatus_ReadyToAskQuestions.Translation: Ce protocole peut être converti en un protocole équivalent à base d’iode en répondant à une série de questions sur la manière dont il est typiquement utilisé.  Une fois la conversion terminée, le nouveau protocole peut être enregistré sous un nouveau nom.

T_IodineWizardStatus_ReadyToConvert_Desc.Source: All questions have been answered, and the protocol can now be converted.
T_IodineWizardStatus_ReadyToConvert_Desc.Translation: È stata fornita una risposta per tutte le domande e ora è possibile convertire il protocollo.

T_IodineWizardStatus_SecondPhaseMustBeSa.Source: The second phase of this protocol must be a saline flush phase.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_SecondPhaseMustBeSa.Translation: La seconda fase di questo protocollo deve essere una fase di lavaggio con soluzione fisiologica.  Questo protocollo non può essere convertito in un protocollo basato sullo idio.  Al momento è possibile convertire solo i protocolli di iniezione per soluzione fisiologica e per mezzo di contrasto bifase.

T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyInjections_D.Source: This protocol has more than one injection and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyInjections_D.Translation: Niniejszy protokół obejmuje więcej niż jedno wstrzyknięcie i nie może zostać skonwertowany na protokół oparty na jodzie.  Wyłącznie proste, dwufazowe protokoły wstrzykiwania środka kontrastowego i soli fizjologicznej mogą zostać teraz skonwertowane.

T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyPhases_Descr.Source: This protocol has more than just two phases and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyPhases_Descr.Translation: Ce protocole comporte plus de deux phases et il ne peut pas être converti en un protocole à base d’iode.  Seuls les protocoles d’injection de produit de contraste et de sérum physiologique biphasiques simples peuvent être convertis pour le moment.

Совместное использование протоколов позволяет добавлять информацию об атрибуции в локальные протоколы и наборы правил для пикового анодного напряжения.
